If you like a bit of luxury on your holiday, probably best avoided.	The only negative is that the rooms are a little on the small side but I would rather comfort, luxury and small then large and not comfortable.	I don't require top-notch luxury if I'm not paying a lot of money.	I do not know if they do this for everyone, not that I'm special, but a neat surprise.	The room was a bit on the small side, but the fixtures were new and stylish.	If you don't have to pay full price for a room (we used a expedia vacation package and got it for cheap) then it might be one of the best deals in Barcelona!